                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": 420,
                              "content": "The heavy obsidian doors of the Vault groan open, dust cascading from the intricate runes carved into their surface. A cold, unnatural breeze sweeps past you, carrying the scent of ozone and ancient parchment.",
